Language: <F P=105> Azeri </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> ["Text" of Azerbaijan Ministry of Defense press service </F>
communique of 27 March] 
  [Text] Our towns along the Armenian border have been 
continuously fired on for three days now. [words indistinct] 
and the enemy has been observed to mass reinforcements and 
armored units in Fizulinskiy Rayon. Azerbaijan's positions in 
that area were fired on with various types of arms yesterday. 
Azerbaijan military units have been taking the necessary 
measures to strengthen their defensive lines and silence the 
enemy fire emplacements. 
  The situation in the other parts of the front line has been 
relatively peaceful. 

